law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 5, sec. 1, effective January 1, 1986. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 24, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky.
